## Key Features

- 📄 **One-click upload** — PDF / DOCX, with magic-byte validation
- ⚡ **Live progress** — per-requirement results stream in real time
- 🎯 **Confidence scoring** — flags low-certainty assessments
- 💡 **Suggested rewrites** — LLM proposes policy wording to close each gap
- 🔌 **Pluggable LLM** — OpenAI GPT-4o (cloud) or Ollama Mistral (local)
- ♻️ **Smart caching** — re-analyzing a document skips parse + embed
- 📊 **Exports** — formatted Excel (Dashboard + Detailed + Summary) and PDF

