## Architecture

```
Browser (HTML + JS)
   │  /api/upload   → store document
   │  /api/analyze  → Server-Sent Events stream
   ▼
FastAPI backend
   ├── parser.py        document → chunks
   ├── embeddings.py    pluggable vector backend
   ├── retrieval.py     FAISS + BM25 hybrid
   ├── reranker.py      cross-encoder / heuristic
   ├── analyzer.py      L1/L2/L3 LLM reasoning
   ├── reporter.py      Excel + PDF generation
   └── cache.py         persistent index cache
```

